title.rendered: Trend Micro Computer Support and Internet Security 2010

content.rendered:
With Computer Support and Internet Security, help is just a phone call away. Trend Micro give you peace of mind, when you need it. For one year, you get a subscription to Trend Micro’s Internet Security software for up to three PCs, as well as 24/7 emergency and live support access to a Trend Micro technical specialist, when you encounter unexpected security problems. Our computer and security experts will work with you to figure out what’s wrong, then connect to your PC over the Internet, and fix it as your watch!
Language ‏ : ‎ English
Package Dimensions ‏ : ‎ 7.5 x 5.4 x 1.2 inches; 7.2 Ounces
Item model number ‏ : ‎ CSIS7318
Date First Available ‏ : ‎ April 22, 2010
Manufacturer ‏ : ‎ Trend Micro
ASIN ‏ : ‎ B003MU9CPE

Protects against computer viruses, worms, Trojan horse programs, and related security threats; anti-spyware technology guards your personal information and privacy against spyware, rootkits, and other malicious software
Steer clear of online phishing scams that try to steal your credit card or bank account numbers; block malicious or untrustworthy hyperlinks in email, websites, or instant messages
Parental controls let you protect your children on the Internet–block websites with inappropriate content, prevent access at specific times, and even stop them from entering personal information onto web pages
PC Tune-up Services speed up the performance of your PC; get help with setting up your PC security, backup and file management, internet and email, etc.
